5th full length project. A tribute to my favorite anime series of all time. I watched it a couple of years ago and it amazed me how cool and badass it was. I would listen to Nujabes and Fat Jon a bit before watching, inspired by their works among others in the community. Once I heard about their contribution to this anime, I immediately had to watch, getting hooked to the story, beats, and all those fight scenes in the process.

I know I'm a bit of a late cat when it comes to finding out about this anime, but this is a tribute to Samurai Champloo, Nujabes, Fat Jon, and the many others who worked on it.

thank you <3 I hope this did it justice.

Artwork and production by me

s/o my friend @ultimis-music for collaborating on one of the tracks with me for this tape, and other friends who gave me feedback on this. I appreciate you, you know who you all are <3

and thank you, the listener, for supporting me over these years. I hope I didn't disappoint

purpose comes to fruition when you find something you love to do. keep that love around and enjoy the journey.
